{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 856492894, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-31 12:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856492601,45974302,1011]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66586092]笔下山河[/uid] (2026-01-31 12:56):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大肘墨鱼块，今天好勤劳啊。<br/>前些天刚看了80年代白银崩盘的历史，CFTC拔网线，美联储加息，亨特兄弟爆仓，没想到这么快又见证历史了。<br/>另外请教一下，稀土永磁后续怎么看？我周四尾盘开超市拿了一点点先手，周五觉得补涨的逻辑虽然没了，但本来就在低位杀的有点过，想等个反弹就没卖。等伊朗打起来，金油修复再传导过来，感觉有点太遥远。还有必要做时间的朋友吗？[/quote]<br/>所有金属的目前的短期逻辑都是金银补涨，按A股的情绪面，我个人是不会去做时间的朋友<br/>石油有别的预期，所以我只留了剩下的石油。<br/>以上仅代表个人。<br/>你们自己能是不是卖在更好的位置，这个要看自己水平了。 我只能说 大部分应该都没有上周5的卖点好。", "lou": 580, "content_length": 231, "reply_to": 856492601, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769835560}, {"pid": 856676414, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 31, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 09:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "石油能清的我就先清了  个股。给的位置不错", "lou": 581, "content_length": 38, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769996092}, {"pid": 856677962, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 93, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 09:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "现在还觉得上周减仓策略有问题吗？", "lou": 582, "content_length": 32, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769996812}, {"pid": 856678370, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 8, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 09:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856678103,45974302,1022]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65743418]不想穿苦茶[/uid] (2026-02-02 09:47):[/b]<br/><br/>鱼大 石油个股是全部跑完吗？[/quote]<br/>我已经说了 我能跑的都跑了  只做期货", "lou": 583, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 856678103, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769997000}, {"pid": 856684524, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 10:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856684084,45974302,1028]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38089706]名字抢光了[/uid] (2026-02-02 10:28):[/b]<br/><br/>按照上周五说的，现在反弹的方向还没确认，不急着加仓吧[/quote]<br/>对的 ，重点不是这里还会不会跌，这个已经是过去式了，重点是 涨什么<br/>所以减仓出来的钱要留着，因为是结构性行情，买不对那也和自己没关系。而且还要被抽血。", "lou": 584, "content_length": 149, "reply_to": 856684084, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769999464}, {"pid": 856684789, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 10:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "包括在别的楼里我也说了，如果真的非常痴迷CPO的 可以借业绩MISS止跌后去抄底  是很有性价比的。<br/>现在确实业绩杀，就等个止跌或者缓速就行了。<br/>我非常明确，没有任何模棱两可", "lou": 585, "content_length": 157, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769999559}, {"pid": 856685455, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 10:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856685238,45974302,1029]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67086272]冷酷鸡腿堡game[/uid] (2026-02-02 10:35):[/b]<br/><br/>请教一个问题，狼大可以盘后回复下么<br/>液冷目前还没有业绩处于0-1，为啥业绩杀也会杀到<br/>等于说还是旭创的映射？[/quote]<br/>因为短期资金和长期资金预期不一样，短期逻辑到了没验证就出场 就这么简单。", "lou": 586, "content_length": 75, "reply_to": 856685238, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769999821}, {"pid": 856686684, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 10:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856686268,45974302,1030]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43310054]是你的哇哈哈[/uid] (2026-02-02 10:41):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，请教一下，根据这个逻辑，现在的主要任务就是：<br/>1、观察盘面有没有系统性风险<br/>2、观察盘面什么时候缩转放止跌<br/>3、观察资金流向哪个板块<br/>上周五减仓的抄早了[s:a2:偷吃][s:a2:偷吃][s:a2:偷吃][/quote]<br/>对啊  现在就是观察", "lou": 587, "content_length": 21, "reply_to": 856686268, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770000271}, {"pid": 856687158, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 43, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 10:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "好了 缩量已经到地量了 。我前面分享过的", "lou": 588, "content_length": 36, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770000455}, {"pid": 856688867, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 137, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 10:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856687957,45974302,1032]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-02-02 10:52):[/b]<br/><br/>不会有兄弟刚刚低点割肉了吧。[s:ac:哭笑]<br/><br/>好像每次都有这样的人。。。[/quote]<br/>鉴于你没那么笨了，我多分享一个<br/>怎么看反弹方向，就是地量后大盘第二次继续缩量的下探 大盘没过前低 这是前提<br/>而观察的板块或者个股也没低于前低 这是基础条件<br/>这时候只有观察有补量向上，那就是反弹方向。越多同方向个股同一个技术走势，那就是反弹板块方向", "lou": 589, "content_length": 239, "reply_to": 856687957, "14": {"13": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770001130}, {"pid": 856691358, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 69, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 11:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "最低没有跌破4064  而且还在继续缩量，我个人绝对不会在这个位置卖任何股票", "lou": 590, "content_length": 68, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770002090}, {"pid": 856692488, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 11:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们自己观察吧  学习是要一点一点来的。人教人学不会，市场会教你们做人的。", "lou": 591, "content_length": 70, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770002515}, {"pid": 856694051, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 11:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856693754,45974302,1037]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41800010]青蛙鸣泣之时1[/uid] (2026-02-02 11:29):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:a2:大哭]好像破了啊[/quote]<br/>那我问你新低能抄底吗？", "lou": 592, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 856693754, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770003088}, {"pid": 856694447, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 61, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 11:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "怎么样才能抄底我觉得我写得非常清楚了 什么条件下才能看反抽的方向我也说了<br/>如果不看 还是这么一惊一乍，那只能是这个市场的肥料，这没有任何办法。", "lou": 593, "content_length": 136, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770003244}, {"pid": 856706344, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 13:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "15分钟上证底背离了 在稍微忍一下 机器人是因为消息", "lou": 594, "content_length": 46, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770008800}, {"pid": 856706589, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 13:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856706457,45974302,1043]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43310054]是你的哇哈哈[/uid] (2026-02-02 13:07):[/b]<br/><br/>擎天柱全靠马总活着了[s:a2:哭][s:a2:哭][s:a2:哭][/quote]<br/>机器人目前就是靠消息啊  所以暂时只做T链，那个天奇就是个股抱团而已了  。", "lou": 595, "content_length": 72, "reply_to": 856706457, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770008935}, {"pid": 856707106, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 57, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 13:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我从来不做  调整行情的消息反抽。因为他一定不是重回趋势<br/>而且这里做很容易把本来灵活的资金套进去。 从而错过大级别的反抽行情", "lou": 596, "content_length": 116, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770009209}, {"pid": 856707787, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 13:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856707436,45974302,1044]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-02-02 13:16):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，今天把见底的情况定义成反抽，是后面到4141左右还会再踩一脚么？[/quote]<br/>如果反抽先看4117啊  跳空下跌肯定以前一天的收盘价为压力 反抽过了才能看能不能反弹。哪有跳过去的", "lou": 597, "content_length": 95, "reply_to": 856707436, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770009574}, {"pid": 856707947, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 13:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856707455,45974302,1044]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60175320]asdfzywzyw[/uid] (2026-02-02 13:16):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，可以请教下您是看的哪个指标判断底背离么？我看15分钟macd没有底背离呀？[/quote]<br/>MACD没有  KDJ应该差不多了", "lou": 598, "content_length": 28, "reply_to": 856707455, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770009657}, {"pid": 856708177, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-02 13:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "conten